### ===== Direkt UserService (local dev - port 8080) =====

### Create User (direct)
POST http://localhost:8080/users/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password",
  "email": "admin@gmail.com"
}

###
### Login (direct)
POST http://localhost:8080/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password"
}

> {%
    client.test("Direct Login - should return token", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 200);
        client.global.set("direct_token", response.body.token);
    });
%}

###
### Get User by ID (direct)
GET http://localhost:8080/users/id/1
Authorization: Bearer {{direct_token}}

